import React, { useEffect } from "react"; // 引入模組 import { LabelSelect, LabelInput, DateInput } from "../../../components/ReactElement/InputCombo" import { ColorBtn } from "../../../components/ReactElement/ColorBtn" import { PageBtnsHader } from "../../../components/ReactElement/OriginalLabel/LabelPageBtns" import { LabelTitleNormal } from "../../../components/ReactElement/OriginalLabel/LabelTitle" import { LabelCheckerboard } from "../../../components/ReactElement/OriginalLabel/LabelCheckerboard" import { PageBtnsFooter } from "../../../components/ReactElement/OriginalLabel/LabelPageBtns" // 引入表格需要的函式 import { ChangeWorld } from "./LabelFunction" import { PageSelect } from "../../../components/ReactElement/OriginalLabel/LabelFunction" export function OrderManagement() { let DataTitle = ["排序", "訂單狀態", "訂單成立時間", "取餐時間", "訂單編號", "主機名稱", "金額", "訂購人", "操作"]; localStorage.setItem("LabelTitleCost", DataTitle.length, 60000) //製造表單標題格數 localStorage.setItem("LabelCotentCost", localStorage.MaxPageValue, 60000) //製造表單欄位格數 useEffect(() => { setTimeout(() => { ChangeWorld(); PageSelect(); }, 100); }); return <> {/* 店家與日期選擇 */}
{/* 表格 */} < PageBtnsHader />
}
